query:
SELECT v.id as video_id, v.fileKey as v_key, f.id as file_id, f.fileKey as f_key 
FROM videos v, files f 
WHERE v.fileKey = f.fileKey AND v.userId = f.userId AND v.fileId IS NULL
LIMIT 10;
